Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 比想像中還要難登
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和日向拚命向山頂前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連葵和楓那份一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\pos(1037,215)}「再也不要了！！」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭疼怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好一點了 不過還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 馬上就要天亮了 日出怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會難得 稍微努力一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面很冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面再穿上些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我跟媽媽借來了羽絨服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點 還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是山頂的鳥居
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 日出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜色漸明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都在看著同一個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺彷彿是一個整體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日出太震驚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了真是太好了 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…為什麼我的身體動不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心 我不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我們到山頂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下了山就會好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上也下山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用急的 機會難得 繞火山口一圈怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繞火山口一圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繞火山口走上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個半小時到兩個小時左右就能繞一圈 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先下到五合目 到了再給你們打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話 我的腳很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 吃了便當以後 去繞火山口一圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便當真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豬肉醬湯也好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山很餓肚子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的消耗能量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要走很久呢 好好補充能量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然剛才還很黑看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有岩石 雲彩 和天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是在天空散步一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涼風好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像僊人掌一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想寫給葵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少把我現在的心情告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我也來寫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點點了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭和腳都很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不走的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以勉強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不露出不悅的表情 卻和我在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我給你添了那麼大的麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終點還在很遠的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算走啊走啊 也完全無法接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候能到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事還要繼續到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「還有多遠呢」你還是不要總想著這樣的事比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越想越總是無法到達哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把腦袋放空 專心走路的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知什麼時候就會到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我明明這麼痛苦卻要登山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼還會來到這種地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳好累 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最後了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍峰 3776米
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是日本的 最高峰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬歲 萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太奇妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山 最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬歲 萬歲 萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬歲 萬歲 萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山 我享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 到了嗎 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐巴士還有時間 去看看土特產怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣呀 下次來請讓我乘坐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我們約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看土特產吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山也很辛苦啊 腳都快斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過刻印全都刻上了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個 葵想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我買給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 巴士快來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和家裏聯繫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想打呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了那麼多任性的話 一定會被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 你都沒聯繫我 我好擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的聲音是怎麼了 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我等下要去坐巴士了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記跟你聯繫了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢 你努力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體沒事吧 能回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 我明明讓你這麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還鼓勵我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道該做出什麼表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太驚奇了 富士山不愧是世界的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭也疼 腳也疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累 我再也不想留下這種回憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大山什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,0)\pos(919,530)}未完待續
